                        <p>In several paragraphs it is not clear which trypanosomes are considered, e.g., when describing chemotherapy and drug resistance it is stated that COMBAT will collect trypanosomes, perform full genome sequencing, and annotation of both resistant and susceptible isolates, followed by comparative analysis. Is the aim to do this for all AT-causing trypanosomes (
