                        <p>The authors state that, as to SDG3, the project will contribute to good health and well-being through new vector control tools and improved diagnostics, which will support the ongoing HAT elimination initiatives.&#x00a0;However, looking at the COMBAT activities, it is not clear how they will support the ongoing HAT-elimination initiatives. Currently, the latter is focused on 
